Third-party code, tracked verbatim.

Upstream: https://github.com/JuliusBrussee/caveman
Vendored: 2026-07-23

This directory is exempt from the workspace size gate (.hooks/check-line-counts.sh and
.hooks/pre-edit.py both read this marker). Splitting these files to satisfy a 200-line
limit would fork them from upstream and make the next update impossible to diff.

Local adaptations are deliberate and documented in CONTEXT.md — keep them small and
listed there so a future re-sync with upstream stays tractable.
